<tr><td><strong>Transfer Pricing Study and Form 3CEB</strong></td><td>Under Section 92 to 92F of the Income-tax Act; ALP determination for inter-corporate transactions; Form 3CEB filing by 31 October under Section 92E.</td><td class="text-center"><span class="badge-addon">Add-on</span></td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Section 129(3) Consolidated Financial Statements</strong></td><td>Consolidated balance sheet, P&amp;L, cash flow; Form AOC-1 attachment; reconciliation across subsidiaries, associates, and joint ventures; Rule 6 Companies (Accounts) Rules 2014 compliance.</td><td class="text-center"><span class="badge-addon">Add-on</span></td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Section 248(2) Voluntary Strike-Off</strong></td><td>Voluntary strike-off via Form STK-2 after the SPV project closes; settlement of liabilities; holding-company shareholder consent.</td><td class="text-center"><span class="badge-addon">Add-on</span></td></tr>


                    </tbody>
                </table>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- SECTION 7: 7-STEP PROCESS -->
<section class="steps-section" id="procedure-section">
    <div class="section-container">
