            <span class="section-eyebrow">Our Process</span>
            <h2 class="section-title">Procedure - Step by Step to Build the Group Structure</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle" style="text-align:left;max-width:100%;">End-to-end workflow from scoping workshop and entity-form selection through SPICe+ incorporation of holding plus SPV, narrow MoA drafting, shareholder agreement, Section 80M and 115BAA election, FEMA inbound or outbound filings, and 12-month compliance calendar.</p>
        </header>
        <div class="steps-container">
            
<div class="step-card">
    <div class="step-content">
        <span class="step-badge">Step 1</span>
        <h3 class="step-title">Scoping Workshop and Structure Design</h3>
        <p class="step-description">Map the business objective (raise, exit, ring-fence, tax, FEMA); shortlist 2 to 3 structure options; model tax and FEMA outcomes for each; freeze the chosen architecture in a one-page structure diagram with each entity tagged to a tax election.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step-visual">
        <div class="step-number-large">01</div>
        <div class="step-illustration">
