        </div>
        <div class="step-label">Structure Frozen</div>
    </div>
</div>


<div class="step-card">
    <div class="step-content">
        <span class="step-badge">Step 2</span>
        <h3 class="step-title">Class 3 DSC and DIN</h3>
        <p class="step-description">Obtain Class 3 Digital Signature Certificate for all proposed directors; apply for Director Identification Number under Section 153 Companies Act, 2013 (existing DINs reused where available).</p>
