        <h3 class="step-title">SPICe+ Part A Name Reservation (Both Entities)</h3>
        <p class="step-description">File SPICe+ Part A on the MCA portal for both the holding company and the SPV; reserve names that signal the parent-subsidiary relationship without infringing existing trademarks.</p>
